per mass limit of 15^{+5}_{-3} M_{sun}\nfor the progenitor. The increased upper limit results mainly from the larger\ndistance derived through the EPM than was assumed by the Smartt et al.\nanalyses, which relied on less precise (and less recent) distance measurements\nto NGC 3184.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Jul 2002 18:40:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
