ial observers would lead to the thermal properties of static patch.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Jul 2002 17:45:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 11 Sep 2002 14:37:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-03-16"}
