ed spheres to its geometric\nstructure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Jul 2002 02:27:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Nov 2002 00:42:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
